      • WINDOW_X

        public static int WINDOW_X
        The parameter WINDOW_X, WINDOW_Y is the coordinate of the up-left corner of the window relative to the computer screen. WINDOW_WIDTH, WINDOW_HEIGHT is the width and height of the window.
